MAP:  sor_deatharena


SOUND OF REVENGE MAP



The map was completely made by me,it's the first one I've ever made.


It has been made for CSS only,to install the map,place the sor_deatharena.bsp in 
C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\<USERNAME>\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps folder.




Then it should be successfully installed and ready to play on.
